WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:11.000
Let's suppose that you were able every night to dream, any dream you wanted to dream.

00:13.000 --> 00:20.000
And you would naturally, as you began on this adventure of dreams, you would fulfill all your wishes.

00:21.000 --> 00:26.000
You would have every kind of pleasure.

00:27.000 --> 00:31.000
And after several nights, you would say, wow, that was pretty great.

00:32.000 --> 00:35.000
But now let's have a surprise.

00:36.000 --> 00:39.000
Let's have a dream which isn't under the cloud.

00:40.000 --> 00:44.000
Well, something is going to happen to me that I don't know what is going to be.

00:46.000 --> 00:52.000
Then you would get more and more adventurous, and you would make further and further out gambles as to what you would dream.

00:52.000 --> 00:57.000
Finally, you would dream where you are now.

